Messages.Value: Thank you for calling Woodgrove Travel agency. My name is Evelyn Perez. How may I assist you today?
Hello, this is John Smith. I recently traveled from Seattle to New York with Contoso Airways and I had a terrible experience.
I'm sorry to hear that, Mr. Smith. Could you please provide me with more details about what happened?
The flight was delayed for hours without any proper explanation. I missed an important meeting because of it. I also found the cabin crew to be rude and unhelpful.
I apologize for the inconvenience you experienced, Mr. Smith. Let me check the details of your flight so I can assist you further.
Thank you, I appreciate your help.
I see that you were scheduled to fly on Contoso Airways flight CA123 from Seattle to New York on September 25, 2022. Is that correct?
I apologize for the inconvenience caused by the delay. Unfortunately, flight delays can occur due to various reasons, including weather conditions or technical issues.
I understand that, but there was no proper communication from the airline regarding the delay. It was frustrating and unprofessional.
I completely understand your frustration, Mr. Smith. I will make a note of your feedback regarding the lack of communication from the airline. Is there something else I can assist you with?
No, that's all for now. I just wanted to express my dissatisfaction with the service.
I appreciate you bringing this to our attention, Mr. Smith. If you have any future travel plans, please don't hesitate to reach out to us for assistance. Have a great day!
